256
00:11:43,025 --> 00:11:43,994
Le scan arrive.

257
00:11:44,114 --> 00:11:46,133
Le voilà, attendez.

258
00:11:46,757 --> 00:11:47,912
Attendez, attendez.

259
00:11:50,370 --> 00:11:52,398
- Attendez.
- Ça ne peut pas être ça.

260
00:11:52,532 --> 00:11:55,198
Je ne vois aucun fluide,

261
00:11:55,398 --> 00:11:57,910
